snippet.title: Gameplay Overview
snippet.description:
Craft a powerful collection of units and powers to use in head-to-head auto battler combat against players worldwide. Outplay your opponent with strategic maneuvers and watch the battle unfold on a tabletop arena. Win matches to climb the ranks and become Godlike!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1480960/Godsbane/
